    <p align="left"><strong>Manuscript and Early Print</strong></p>
    <p>London, British Library, MS Additional 61823 (Sole surviving manuscript witness for 
      <em>The Book of Margery Kempe</em>).</p>
    <p><em>Here begynneth a shorte treatyse of contemplacyon taught by our lorde Jhesu cryste, or </em>
      <em>taken out of the boke of Margerie kempe of lyn[n].</em> London: Wynkyn de Worde, 
      1501 (STC 14924).</p>
