      Book of Margery Kempe, Ancress of Lynn.” In <em>The Cell of Self-Knowledge: </em>
  <em>seven Early English Mystical Treatises printed by Henry Pepwell mcxxi</em>. Ed. 
      Edmund G. Gardner. London: Henry Pepwell, 1521 (STC 20972).</p>
